kau ada di sini.

177
00:09:56,200 --> 00:09:58,750
Kami butuh bantuanmu, segera.

178
00:10:01,370 --> 00:10:02,790
Jangan ke mana-mana.

179
00:10:04,880 --> 00:10:06,539
